seo: swagger,api泄露,敏感信息,未授权访问,插件
summary: 该插件用于扫描Swagger API路径，检测是否存在Swagger UI泄露以及返回的JSON中是否包含敏感信息泄露。同时支持多个URL的异步扫描。
summary_en: This plugin scans Swagger API paths to detect Swagger UI exposure and sensitive information leaks in the returned JSON. It also supports asynchronous scanning of multiple URLs.
